The Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence offered by 4Geeks Academy is a 6-week program designed for professionals looking to integrate AI into their current roles. The course covers various topics, including the different types of generative AI, context, prompts, and models. It includes 2 live online classes per week and has a maximum class size of 12 people. By completing the course, participants will gain essential tools and best practices to strategically implement AI in their workplace. No previous experience is required. Participants will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. For more information, visit: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop